data.value:
This is James Hudson's attempt at the "ONeillo v1.0" application. It was developed by Dr Peter O'Neill of Sheffield Hallam University, for his level four students on the module, "Programming for Computing"
This ""ONeillo v 1.0" application uses all the techniques explained and demonstrated throughout the course.
THe GUIImageArray used within the application was provided to the students.
